<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>로그인</title>
    <link
            rel="stylesheet"
            href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css"
    />
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <link
            href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
            rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link
            rel="stylesheet"
            href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"
    />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/login.css"/>
    <link
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR&display=swap"
            rel="stylesheet"
    />
</head>

{{> layout/header}}
<form action="/login" method="post">
    <div class="felx-box">
        <div class="login-container">
            <div>
                <h1>쉽게 가입하고<br/>간편하게 로그인하세요.</h1>
                <p>일하는 사람들의 모든 가능성, 원티드</p>
            </div>

            <input
                    class="input-box"
                    type="email"
                    placeholder="이메일을 입력해주세요."
                    name="email"
                    value="ssar@nate.com"
            />
            <input
                    class="input-box"
                    type="password"
                    placeholder="비밀번호를 입력해주세요."
                    name="password"
                    value="1234"
            />

            <div class="options">
                <label><input type="checkbox"/> 로그인 유지</label>
                <div class="radio-group">
                    <label
                    ><input type="radio" name="type" checked/>
                        구직자</label
                    >
                    <label><input type="radio" name="type"/> 기업</label>
                </div>
            </div>

            <button class="submit-btn btn btn-primary">이메일로 계속하기</button>

            <div class="links">
                <a href="/join-form">회원가입</a>
                <!--<div>
                    <a href="#">계정 찾기</a>
                    <a href="#">비밀번호 찾기</a>
                </div>-->
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</form>
{{> layout/footer}}
